    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A period in Japanese culture lasting from 1688-1704 that marks the high point of Edo period culture. This period is known for its advanced art and literary production. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
